HEADWORD: Fungic
<hw>Fun"gic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L. <ets>fungus</ets>
mushroom: cf. F. <ets>fungique</ets>, <ets>fongique</ets>.]</ety>
